OL,5, The leader of the Taliban has ordered  
OL,6, Afghan officials to sack relatives they
OL,7, have hired to government positions.    
OL,9,FHibatullah Akhundzada's decree says    
OL,10,Fofficials should replace appointed sons
OL,11,For other family members - and refrain  
OL,12,Ffrom hiring relatives in future.       
OL,14,FThe Taliban dismissed some senior staff
OL,15,Fwhen they took power in 2021, while    
OL,16,Fothers fled.                           
OL,18,FThere have been allegations that       
OL,19,Finexperienced staff have been hired    
OL,20,Fbased on their personal connections.   
